GeneralFileReader - Class in files
Provides a file reading utility class to read from an input file, specified by its filename, and store the resulting data in a String array.
GeneralFileReader(String) - Constructor for class files.GeneralFileReader
Creates a reader with methods to read the file specified by the passed filename as well as to return the data read from the file in the form of a String array.
getFileName() - Method in class files.GeneralFileReader
Utility method to return the filename currently specified for use by the reader.
getHashAlgo() - Method in class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
Returns a string, as imported from the input file, with the name of the algorithm used to generate the hash of the file data which was included with the file itself.
getImportedHash() - Method in class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
Returns a string, as imported from the input file, which represents the value of the hash that was included with the file.
getIt() - Method in class files.GeneralFileReader
Method to return the data read from the file by the readIt() method, this method requires that the readIt() method is called first.
getPubKeyAlgo() - Method in class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
Returns a string, as imported from the input file, with the name of the algorithm used to generate the public key for the player represented by the input file.
getPubKeyFileName() - Method in class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
Returns a string, as imported from the input file, with the name of the key file holding the public key of the player represented by the input file.
getPvtKeyAlgo() - Method in class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
Returns a string, as imported from the input file, with the name of the algorithm used to generate the private key for the player represented by the input file.
getPvtKeyFileName() - Method in class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
Returns a string, as imported from the input file, with the name of the key file holding the private key of the player represented by the input file.
getUID() - Method in class files.PlayerInformationFileInterpreter
Returns the value of the UID imported from the input file.
GroupCompInitializationFileInterpreter - Class in files
 
GroupCompInitializationFileInterpreter(String) - Constructor for class files.GroupCompInitializationFileInterpreter
Creates a file reader specific to importing data for initializing the Group Computation from the specified file.
